### POST /api/v1/payments
### Descripción: Crear pago para un viaje completado. Requiere JWT (pasajero) + Idempotency-Key.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>, Idempotency-Key: <string>
### Códigos: 200 OK (PaymentDto) | 400 IDEMPOTENCY_KEY_REQUIRED, TRIP_NOT_COMPLETED | 403 | 503 PAYMENT_GATEWAY_ERROR

# @name createPayment
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
Idempotency-Key: payment-{{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tripId": "{{TRIP_ID}}",
  "amount": 15.00,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### Response esperado (200):
# {
#   "id", "tripId", "amount", "currency", "status", "createdAtUtc", "clientSecret" (opcional)
# }

### Response error (400): IDEMPOTENCY_KEY_REQUIRED, TRIP_NOT_COMPLETED, UNAUTHORIZED_PAYMENT
### Response error (503): PAYMENT_GATEWAY_ERROR
